    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1928-05-25T14:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1928-05-25T14:00:00-05:00" n="299"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d299">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">881.00/1408: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Frame</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Herrick</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-05-25T20:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 25, 1928—8 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 8:35 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>134. My 95, April 14, 1 p.m.<note n="24" xml:id="d299fn24">Not printed.</note>
                    Associated Press corroborates reported Tangier agreement reached yesterday. In
                    addition Foreign Office informs me that when eventually signed it will be
                    communicated to all signatories to Act of Algeciras.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herrick</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
